FT  17 DEC 93 / UK Company News: Park Food in Pounds 9.3m expansion
Park Food Group, which specialises in supplying Christmas hampers via a
network of commission-paid agents direct to homes, has paid Pounds 9.3m for
Handling Solutions, a promotions management company.
The consideration is being satisfied by the issue of new Park shares worth
about Pounds 800,000 and the balance of Pounds 8.5m through the issue of
10-year variable rate guaranteed redeemable loan notes.
